         ?  Screaming guitar feedback made easy                    ?
         ?                                                         ?
         ?  Release  your inner  beast with  the first  realistic  ?
         ?  guitar  feedback  simulator on  the  market. Go  from  ?
         ?  moderate and subtle to rampant and wild by the  twist  ?
         ?  of a knob (or two). To break new musical ground,  try  ?
         ?  inputting  a  synthesizer,  a  violin,  or  even your  ?
         ?  mother?s grand piano.                                  ?
         ?                                                         ?
         ?                                                         ?
         ?  Features                                               ?
         ?                                                         ?
         ?  Realistic  simulation (physical  modeling) of  guitar  ?
         ?  feedback.                                              ?
         ?                                                         ?
         ?  Fully responsive to vibratos, bends, slides, tremolos  ?
         ?  etc.                                                   ?
         ?                                                         ?
         ?  Simple  user  interface: Control  amount  of feedback  ?
         ?  with the  Feedback knob,  and the  sensitivity with a  ?
         ?  Tolerance knob.                                        ?
         ?                                                         ?
         ?  Compatible with foot controls via MIDI                 ?
         ?                                                         ?
         ?  Includes a stripped*,  but extremely useful,  version  ?
         ?  of the White amp from Vintage Amp Room.                ?
